title: 1972 Salvadoran Primera División
text: The 1972 Primera División was the 31st season of the <a href="Primera%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20de%20F%C3%BAtbol%20de%20El%20Salvador">Primera División de Fútbol de El Salvador</a>, the top tier of <a href="Association%20football">football</a> in <a href="Football%20in%20El%20Salvador">El Salvador</a>. <a href="C.D.%20%C3%81guila">C.D. Águila</a> won their 6th national title.
